From 3f6201a1cfe29f4138fe9aef241bda8d7ed42fa7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Luccifer <gleb.karp@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 17:27:57 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add vagina enchanting, /sex battles and dick-thief gnomes

- /ench and /enchb: Lineage 2 style enchanting for players at <= 0 cm
  (safe up to ENCH_SAFE_LEVEL, then a non-linear chance driven by the
  total mass of positive dicks in the chat; a failure resets to +0,
  a blessed failure keeps the level)
- /bless: the Vagina of the Day election granting bless scrolls
- /sex: a 50/50 battle of a sharpened vagina versus a dick; the vagina
  bites the dick off and becomes one, or gets dulled to +0 while the
  winner receives half the sharpness as blesses
- dick-thief gnomes: a daily weighted-roulette raid on one player with
  a dick longer than GNOMES_MIN_LENGTH per chat, announced at
  GNOMES_RAID_HOUR_UTC
- all parameters are configurable via environment variables
